Cliffjumper/Beachcomber

Cliffjumper looked astonished, they had just lost Firedrill, who knew where
he went. Now Cliffjumper saw an awesome and horrifying beast. "What the?"
he said transforming into his car mode, and motoring off towards it.
"Cliffjumper, no, this isnt our fight." Beachcomber exclaimed. Cliffjumper
was to far though. He didnt know who the robot being ripped in half was,
but he didnt want to see someone die such a painful death. He hit a jump,
and proppeled himself towards Prowl (He dosent know it's Prowl), and
transforms, to try to land on the beasts back.
